    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">The ASR Outdoor sifting sieves are great starter sifting tools for kids and beginners who are just getting started with metal detecting and beachcombing. It comes in 4 different vibrant colors (sold separately) - blue, green, yellow, or red. These sifting pans are designed to easily sift materials out of black sand, dirt, and silt while metal detecting. They each have a diameter of 8.5” so they’ll fit on top of most standard buckets used while metal detecting or beach-combing for sand dollars and beach glass. With built-in handles, the sifting sieves are made of durable, high-quality plastic that won’t rust so you can count on it rain or shine</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">ASR Outdoor Sand Sifting Beach Combing Kids Metal Detector Accessory - 4 Colors</h2>\n  <p>The ASR Outdoor sifting sieves are great starter sifting tools for kids and beginners who are just getting started with metal detecting and beachcombing. It comes in 4 different vibrant colors (sold separately) - blue, green, yellow, or red.</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li>8.5” DIAMETER SIFTING SIEVE - The ASR Outdoor sand sifting classifying screen is a beach-combing essential. These sifting pans are designed to easily sift sand dollars and beach glass out of sand, silt, and dirt. The small size makes this ideal for kids too!</li>\n    <li>STACKABLE DESIGN - With built-in handles, these sifting sieves are meant to sit on top of a bucket or other classifying tool while beach-combing. It’s made of durable, high-quality plastic that won’t rust so you can count on it in unfavorable weather conditions.</li>\n    <li>36 HOLES PER SQUARE INCH - Each sifter features 36 holes per square inch, making it a medium-coarse to fine sifting tool. This means it will sort valuable items while sifting out other unwanted materials.</li>\n    <li>ESSENTIAL BEGINNER’S BEACH-COMBING TOOL - These are great starter sifting tools for kids and beginners who are just getting started with this hobby. It comes in 4 different vibrant colors (sold separately) - blue, green, yellow, or red. They can also be used for building sandcastles and other beach time pretend play.</li>\n    <li><strong>SPECIFICATIONS - Material:</strong> plastic; Colors: blue, green, yellow, or red; Holes per square inch: 36; Stackable design; Handles included; yes; Diameter: 8.5”</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/DOWS_products/1000x1000/sports_outdoors/gold_panning/classifiers/GP4-94P_1_stock7.jpg\" alt=\"The ASR Outdoor sifting sieves are great starter sifting tools for kids and beginners who are just getting started with metal detecting\" style=\"max-width:100%;width:600px;height:auto\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Product Specifications</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>MPN:</strong> ASROSS4CM</li>\n    <li><strong>UPC:</strong> 810058485939</li>\n    <li><strong>Size:</strong> Single</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p>These sifting pans are designed to easily sift materials out of black sand, dirt, and silt while metal detecting. They each have a diameter of 8.5” so they’ll fit on top of most standard buckets used while metal detecting or beach-combing for sand dollars and beach glass.</p>\n  <p>With built-in handles, the sifting sieves are made of durable, high-quality plastic that won’t rust so you can count on it rain or shine. Take it with you while camping or hiking near rivers, lakes, and beaches!</p>\n  <p>Each sifter features 36 holes per square inch, which will allow it to sift through medium-coarse to fine materials. Beach-combing and building sandcastles are great outdoor activities for adults and kids alike, so grab one of these stackable sieves before your next beach adventure!</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 0\"><img src=\"https://s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/DOWS_photobucket/Shopify_Prop65graphic.jpg\" alt=\"California Proposition 65 warning\" style=\"display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" height=\"78\" width=\"273\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:18px 0 0;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;font-size:13px;color:#777;text-align:center\">&copy; 2026 Deals Only Web Store</p>\n</div>",
